+/**
+ * drm_dp_get_dual_mode_type_name - Get the name of the DP dual mode adaptor type as a string
+ * @type: DP dual mode adaptor type
+ *
+ * Returns:
+ * String representation of the DP dual mode adaptor type
+ */
